// RES-4134: repro for the two new JIT builtins (abs_diff, sign).
// Neither had a Cranelift shim before this ticket, so calling them
// hit the JIT's "call to unknown function" catch-all. Uses an
// explicit top-level `return` — see println_string.rz's comment.
println(abs_diff(10, 3));
println(sign(-5));
return 0;
